OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump has posted
OL,8,Fan AIgenerated image of himself
OL,9,Fholding a rifle, escalating his
OL,10,Fthreats towards Iran as he accused the
OL,11,Fregime of stalling in nuclear
OL,12,Fnegotiations and failing to advance
OL,13,Ftowards a deal.
OL,15,FPosting on his Truth Social, the
OL,16,Fpresident said the regime "can't get
OL,17,Fits act together" and doesn't know
OL,18,F"how to sign a non-nuclear deal".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
