OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777479067
OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FAlongside the message, Trump posted an
OL,8,FAI-generated image of himself holding
OL,9,Fa weapon, with explosions in the
OL,10,Fbackground. The image included the
OL,11,Fstrapline "No more Mr Nice Guy!"
OL,13,FTalks between the US and Iran on
OL,14,Fending the war have stalled in recent
OL,15,Fdays, and a fragile ceasefire remains
OL,16,Fin place.
OL,18,FPakistan's Prime Minister Shehbaz
OL,19,FSharif said Wednesday his government
OL,20,Fis continuing efforts to help ease
OL,21,Ftensions between the US and Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
