OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FIran's Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,8,Fvisited Pakistan over the weekend
OL,9,Fduring the ceasefire, where another
OL,10,Fextended round of talks took place
OL,11,Fbetween Iran and Pakistan.
OL,13,FAraghchi later travelled to Oman and
OL,14,Fthen departed for Russia, where he met
OL,15,Fwith Russian President Vladimir Putin.
OL,17,FAccording to the Russian state news
OL,18,Fagency Tass, Putin praised the Iranian
OL,19,Fpeople as "bravely and heroically
OL,20,Ffighting for their sovereignty".
