OL,7,FHe said Russia would do everything
OL,8,Fpossible to bring peace to the Middle
OL,9,FEast, Tass reported.
OL,11,FPakistan has said it is seeking to
OL,12,Fhost a second round of talks between
OL,13,Fthe United States and Iran.
OL,15,FThe US said it has been clear in peace
OL,16,Fnegotiations that Iran's nuclear
OL,17,Fprogramme must be dealt with from the
OL,18,Foutset.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
