OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FOn Monday, officials told CNN that
OL,8,Freopening the Strait of Hormuz - a
OL,9,Fvital shipping lane which would
OL,10,Ftypically see 200 oil and gas tankers
OL,11,Fpass through it on a normal day -
OL,12,Fwithout resolving questions about
OL,13,FTehran's nuclear programme would
OL,14,Fremove a key piece of America's
OL,15,Fleverage.
OL,17,FTrump claims King 'agrees' Iran should
OL,18,Fnot have nuclear weapon
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
