OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FTrump, during a speech at the White
OL,8,FHouse state dinner on Tuesday,
OL,9,Finsisted the King agreed with him that
OL,10,FIran should never be allowed nuclear
OL,11,Fweapons.
OL,13,F"We're doing a little Middle East work
OL,14,Fright now... and we're doing very
OL,15,Fwell," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
