OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777479067
OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,F"We have militarily defeated that
OL,8,Fparticular opponent, and we're never
OL,9,Fgoing to let that opponent ever.
OL,10,FCharles agrees with me even more than
OL,11,FI do; we're never going to let that
OL,12,Fopponent have a nuclear weapon.
OL,14,F"They know that, and they've known it
OL,15,Fright now, very powerfully."
OL,17,FThe remarks risk drawing the monarch
OL,18,Finto a political row over the conflict
OL,19,Fin the Middle East.
