OL,3,C'No more Mr Nice Guy': Trump shares AI
OL,4,Cpicture of himself in new threat to
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FIn response to Trump's comments, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson from the Palace said:
OL,9,F"The King is naturally mindful of his
OL,10,FGovernment's long-standing and well-
OL,11,Fknown position on the prevention of
OL,12,Fnuclear proliferation."
OL,14,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth will
OL,15,Fface questioning from members of
OL,16,FCongress on Wednesday, for the first
OL,17,Ftime since the US-Iran conflict began.
